{"tid":1994574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「一決高下系列」電影最強特工","createTime":"2020-04-29T14:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T05:39:26.000Z","uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"42e8d9e12c37d73801d7dd7f0a7a743a6f0d972f","tid":1994574,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CU7H7Uw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCU7H7Uw.jpg&h=6486c040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2nZBPdh9_Jc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2nZBPdh9_Jc&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=85db347c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2nZBPdh9_Jc</a><br />\n<br />\nEthan Hunt <br />\n首先輩份最高既<br />\n最勁應該係10幾年來比人背叛再背叛再背叛.....<br />\n都死唔去既特工<br />\n（成日換女 溝女多過做任務）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p28gsUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp28gsUy.jpg&h=259a2ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rsuNowyCF0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrsuNowyCF0c&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=7f28292a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rsuNowyCF0c</a><br />\nJohn wick<br />\n小學雞用鉛筆去插人既特工<br />\n（連隻狗都保護唔到）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9RE97V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9RE97V.jpg&h=4f25efd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7pP3K-yZEug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7pP3K-yZEug&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=2fa7119c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7pP3K-yZEug</a><br />\nDuncan Vizla <br />\n後起之秀 同John wick一樣手起刀落 <br />\n直接最有效率殺人唔搞花俏野既特工<br />\n(連自己隻狗都殺埋）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0VeY1g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0VeY1g.jpg&h=38c00856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ppXCTdGfrK8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FppXCTdGfrK8&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b6e6f7d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ppXCTdGfrK8</a><br />\nBryan Mills<br />\n嘴炮最勁既特工<br />\n可以短時間做好多野同周圍走<br />\n（但個女成日比人捉走）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n+多幾件應該可以整個 特工聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33040378a9938ecc7e5f9d4af4dc541c01cde656","tid":1994574,"uid":42246,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"Ethan Hunt 支持者 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42100c211358b44fd235084853cd3b3a40faa2a","tid":1994574,"uid":42246,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"John wick 支持者 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f54e4595067f98cec3499a563aa954ed6b6498","tid":1994574,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"Duncan Vizla  支持者 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2009d05f405ebe8d9dd883c47873688da5e418","tid":1994574,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"Bryan Mills 支持者 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h